We've got
four kids, Mouch.

93
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:41,040
I was counting on my sperm
being too tired

94
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,580
to make the swim.

95
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,340
Well, I'm gonna
head inside

96
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:45,810
and check the levels
on the hot chocolate.

97
00:04:45,810 --> 00:04:48,880
Yeah, I'm gonna
provide back-up.

98
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:55,060
You know, my grandmother
had this garage door

99
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,820
